column5: Step back in time. Enjoy 1950 Vintage Cabins adjacent to Lake LBJ.  Totally restored and fully furnished 1 bedroom cabins with free cable and WiFi. The only Vintage restored cabins on LBJ. Located on Lake LBJ in Llano County, this region is a beautiful recreation and tourist area close to Marble Falls and Austin. There are so many things to come for. Come for the Hunting/Fishing or just relaxing Winter Getaways. Everything is here, ready for your winter visit. $1000.00 returnable deposit fee
